Axiom axs_Odisj_l : forall a x : E, In x (Odisj_l a) <-> (exists y : E, In y a /\ x = couple y Vide).
Axiom axs_Odisj_r : forall a x : E, In x (Odisj_r a) <-> (exists y : E, In y a /\ x = couple y (singleton Vide)).
Definition Osomme_disj (a b : E) := union (Odisj_l a) (Odisj_r b).
Definition disj_l (a : E) := subset (fun y : E => exists x : E, y = couple x Vide /\ In x a) (cartesien a (singleton Vide)).
Definition disj_r (a : E) := subset (fun y : E => exists x : E, y = couple x (singleton Vide) /\ In x a) (cartesien a (singleton (singleton Vide))).
Definition somme_disj (a b : E) := union (disj_l a) (disj_r b).
Lemma lem_OaN : forall a b : E, somme_disj a b = Osomme_disj a b.

Inductive isTupple : nat -> E -> Prop := | c_0_tupple : isTupple 0 Vide | c_1_tupple : forall a : E, isTupple 1 a | c_2_tupple : forall a b : E, isTupple 2 (couple a b) | c_n_tupple : forall (a b : E) (n : nat), isTupple (S (S n)) b -> isTupple (S (S (S n))) (couple a b).
Fixpoint cart_power (m : nat) : E -> E := fun a : E => match m with | O => Vide | S O => a | S (S n as N) => cartesien a (cart_power N a) end.
Lemma cart_power_eq1 : forall a : E, cart_power 0 a = Vide.
Lemma cart_power_eq2 : forall a : E, cart_power 1 a = a.
Lemma cart_power_eq3 : forall (n : nat) (a : E), cart_power (S (S n)) a = cartesien a (cart_power (S n) a).
Lemma lem_eq_cart_power : forall a : E, cart_power 2 a = cartesien a a.
intros; rewrite (cart_power_eq3 0 a); rewrite (cart_power_eq2 a); reflexivity.
